<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="debate-n">debate <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'beɪt/    美 /dɪ'beɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 讨论；辩论；争论：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>open / close a debate 
开始/终止辩论</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>under debate</strong> 
在讨论/辩论中</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There is <strong>a fierce</strong> / <strong>heated debate about</strong> / <strong>on</strong> / <strong>over</strong> the question whether the experiment should be allowed.
在是否进行这个实验的问题上展开了激烈的争论。</p></div></div>